"They don't make 'em like me anymore."

Ah, one of my oldest obsessions: Razr. V3 to be exact. 
I can't help but dream Neo Tokyo-ish scenarios when I think about a Razr v3. Had to use my favorite color on this. I mean, hey, Paris Hilton had one with her favorite color on it. How could you hate?

13 editions in honor of it's 13.9mm thickness.
